com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.contract

Class ContractExecuteTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.HederaCall<com.hedera.hashgraph.proto.Transaction,com.hedera.hashgraph.proto.TransactionResponse,TransactionId,T>
      • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.TransactionBuilder<ContractExecuteTransaction>
        • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.contract.ContractExecuteTransaction

  • public final class ContractExecuteTransaction
extends TransactionBuilder<ContractExecuteTransaction>
    Call a function in the contract, updating its internal state in the hashgraph. After execution, call Transaction.getRecord(Client) and TransactionRecord.getContractExecuteResult() to get the result of the function call.
